Shoe Dept: Shop Shoes, Boots, Heels, and Sneakers Galore
It’ll be hard to contain your excitement once you’ve seen all of the shoes offered here at JCPenney. Finding the perfect footwear for every walk of life has just gotten simpler than ever! Working up a sweat at the gym or out on the pavement? Grab a pair of cushioned and supportive athletic shoes to help amp up your workouts. Transition into the rest of the day with our extensive array of walking shoes. Pick up some dress shoes or heels to look great in the office or at more formal occasions. When the weather turns sunny, be sure to take a look at our stock of sandals and flip flops. And don’t forget to gear up with a sturdy and stylish pair of boots for those colder months.

Stylish Shoes for Women
Is your shoe rack looking a little empty? Never fear—we’ve got all the right shoes and footwear for women to put the finishing touches on all of your favorite outfits. Whether you’re looking to make a statement or just stay comfy and casual, there’s something for everyone. Enjoy browsing our selection of comfy flats, heels and pumps, boots and sandals and flip flops. Shop women's shoes.

Men’s Shoes for Every Occassion
We’ve got all of your men’s footwear needs covered. From high-performing running shoes for men to the most handsome of men’s dress shoes, you’ll be able to pick up whatever sort of shoe that’ll fit the bill. Enjoy top-notch selection at great prices—comfort and style are just a click away. Shop men's shoes.

Cute and Playful Kids’ Shoes
Even though the little ones are growing so fast, it’s a good idea to get them well-fitting footwear to make sure they’re always comfy and content. Shop our wide variety of shoes for boys and girls with styles ranging from practical and comfortable to dressy and formal. Shop kids' shoes.





		
