ich means everyone can put their best foot forward. Ladies, strut your stuff in daring stilettos or comfy flats. Fellas, buy a dapper pair dress shoes for work. Teens will rave over our super trendy shoes for juniors, and you’ll love the cute shoes we have for the little ones. Shop all the hottest shoe brands around!Learn MoreHandbags & AccessoriesYour beautiful outfits deserve equally as beautiful accessories and handbags! Our handbags and acessories department features classic and trendy styles from amazing brands. At JCPenney, you can find the perfect evening clutch and stylish everyday bag all in one place and at affordable prices. Complete your look with sunglasses, belts, hair accessories and more!Learn MoreJCPenney on instagramfollow usfollow usJCPenney Department Store Vallco Shopping MallCupertino, CAAbout JCPenneyAbout JCPenneyWhatever you’re shopping for, the Vallco Shopping Mall JCPenney department store has looks you’ll love at amazing prices. Like all your favorite brands of apparel, shoes and accessories for women, men and children. And when it comes to finding the perfect fit, we've got the whole family covered there, too. Shop misses, plus, petite, tall and maternity clothing for women. Find a wide selection of big and tall in our men’s store in Cupertino, California. And shop slim, plus and husky sizes for kids. We even offer extended sizes in shoes. Look great from head to toe—and outfit your home from top to bottom with our inspiring selection of home decor, furniture, bedding and housewares. From everyday essentials to affordable luxury, you’ll find everything you need to make your home comfortable, functional and a unique expression of your personal style. Visit your Vallco Shopping Mall, Cupertino, California JCPenney department store for styles that flatter and prices that wow. Shop JCPenney.comCollapse1.800.322.1189customer servicestore servicesmore ways to shopabout uslegalprivacy policyyour California privacy rightsproduct recallssite mapA