www.jcpenney.com

How to use a JCPenney Coupon:Enter the promo code found on DealCatcher.com in the "Coupons & Rewards" section on the shopping cart page. Click "Apply" and discount will be displayed just below in the "Pricing Summary" section prior to checkout.Tips & Tricks:Consider getting a JCP Card if you are a frequent shopper. Just for signing up, you will receive an extra 15% off which can be combined with other offers. In addition, you'll receive a free birthday gift on your birthday, exclusive offers and special bonuses. Just make sure you pay your card off each month to avoid paying late fees & interest.Want to know the secret to finding all the JCPenney coupons? Join their newsletter, scour their ads, look through mailers and visit the main page of their site. If you don't feel like doing all of that, just stop by DealCatcher.com and we'll do all of that for you, for free.

